head.hi:
Notes on a Conference Held between the British Mission to the United States Headed by Mr. Balfour; the Secretary of War;
                        and Representatives of the War Department and the General Munitions Board in
                        May, 1917

div.p:
The subjects listed for conference were: 
                        (a)

Expeditionary Force;
                        (b)

Date of departure of said force;


                        (c)

Types of guns and ammunition;
                        (d)

Recruitments;
                        (e)

Military information;
                        (f)

Shipping.
